  "body": "Currently we are using git tags with a format of `build-[0-9]+` to globally track build numbers which are then used in metadata for Android and iOS builds. They have to be long integers, they have to be incremented, and they cannot clash across multiple builds.\r\n\r\nThis is also related to us wanting to release the app on GitHub, but the \"Releases\" section is cluttered up with `build-*` tags.\r\nRelated: https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/6273",
